OL,5, Sir Richard Branson has said he feared 
OL,6, he was going to lose his entire        
OL,7, business empire during the pandemic.   
OL,9,FThe British businessman said he found a
OL,10,Fmedia backlash "painful" after the     
OL,11,FVirgin Group asked the UK government   
OL,12,Ffor a loan to save the company.        
OL,14,FGiven his personal wealth and home on a
OL,15,FCaribbean island, he was criticised for
OL,16,Fasking for a bailout when airline      
OL,17,FVirgin Atlantic hit trouble.           
OL,19,FSir Richard told the BBC he personally 
OL,20,Flost around #1.5bn during the pandemic.
